  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "Otrium FX chain demo — Cyclical topology with tempo-sync. The triangle rotates continuously across cycles via a separate drift-phase accumulator running at 1/8 the LFO rate, so the panned partners (left / center / right) never collapse into a static pattern. 0.5 cycles-per-beat in Sync mode at 120 BPM = ultra-slow 1 Hz rotation. The pad walks around itself indefinitely. Otrium config embedded under OpenSky's parameter block.",
